{"id": "regional-channels--espa-a-castell-n-valencia", "title": "ESPAÑA, Castellón/Valencia", "forum": "regional-channels", "messages": [{"id": "1400191042929557534", "author": "Gronfiz", "author_handle": "gronfiz", "user_id": "476640013992329249", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/476640013992329249/fa2e530c97f2d63cdd1885075d214986.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, July 30, 2025 2:59 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-07-30 2:59 p.m.", "text": "Intentando aprender y crear una comunidad Meshcore.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Intentando aprender y crear una comunidad  Meshcore.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1428094263262052386", "author": "MAD_Mesh", "author_handle": "mad.mesh", "user_id": "1417407713645826149", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1417407713645826149/89be8598f07ac64e4e65d694b5c79e47.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, October 15, 2025 2:56 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-15 2:56 p.m.", "text": "Hi! How are things in Valencia? Any progress? I am doing test in the north of Madrid", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hi!\nHow are things in Valencia? Any progress?\nI am doing test in the north of Madrid</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1448053290700112062", "author": "Gronfiz", "author_handle": "gronfiz", "user_id": "476640013992329249", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/476640013992329249/fa2e530c97f2d63cdd1885075d214986.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, December 9, 2025 3:46 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-09 3:46 p.m.", "text": "En Valencia hay poca actividad Mesh y Mestastic está colapsado con las tramas de las estaciones meteorológicas.... ah! y no digas nada a los de la radiosecta de URE de que la están cagando que se enfadan.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>En Valencia hay poca actividad Mesh   y Mestastic est&#225; colapsado con las tramas de las estaciones meteorol&#243;gicas....  ah!  y no digas nada a los  de la radiosecta de URE de que la est&#225;n cagando que se enfadan.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=fire><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🔥 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f525.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1448208033137033247", "author": "MAD_Mesh", "author_handle": "mad.mesh", "user_id": "1417407713645826149", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1417407713645826149/89be8598f07ac64e4e65d694b5c79e47.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, December 10, 2025 2:01 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-10 2:01 a.m.", "text": "We have over 10 solar nodes installed around Madrid and they are meshing. So we can comunicate for +30km. Few more will be installed in the following weeks. But we are alone. No others are active yet. We are also trying to popularise this platform. We will see how it goes. Good luck in Valencia!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>We have over 10 solar nodes installed around Madrid and they are meshing. So we can comunicate for +30km. Few more will be installed in the following weeks. But we are alone. No others are active yet. We are also trying to popularise this platform. We will see how it goes. Good luck in Valencia!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454037279860461752", "author": "BobCat", "author_handle": "bobcat894", "user_id": "1438255580052586526", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Friday, December 26, 2025 4:05 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-26 4:05 a.m.", "text": "Pasaros por el grupo de Telegram de España de la comunidad Meshcore, https://t.me/mcoreXAT", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Pasaros por el grupo de Telegram de Espa&#241;a de la comunidad Meshcore, <a href=\"https://t.me/mcoreXAT\">https://t.me/mcoreXAT</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://t.me/mcoreXAT><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">MESHCORE SPAIN</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">Grupo dedicado a promocionar el uso de Meshcore en Espa&#241;a</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/DVtbmwEAGSRLDLsC64O1aVPb90HPKCG-anWhWp-6rxY/https/cdn4.telesco.pe/file/PN6W4idx-WhAMpbFJ35d7iLPM53YspEAgAYXSl7Tp-9gG5k-OEfESlr1HNeuyohAgsu5QNyg-TwAsDglFNljIzV9plHUPJm7NSklCt_BwBV5KJVtojvE10h3OF4vT0GA8xtMGT1ZcBSbnqwLwY7Kl8YuuDQH8Mf32Vt2f2dw4FlzVZ8wm44DU3qaVRRtmQ3Cm-r0Al4-nBNwJs7zq20kiybrNo2aRavHEKgUdZM-rF1xU0yUE_9SEJj7YXYAoZnNbVewsYrLM5_GUsob_HO7sVYwRE2ZABXV6GD13TQ124pXqXArZCyBcWJEk89gyBBYu6ri-AorMArMINFSlPGnRg.jpg> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail 